data.description: Introducing a fully remodeled duplex, a prime investment opportunity in Conway. This property has undergone a complete transformation, featuring two immaculate units, each with two bedrooms, a modern kitchen, and stylish bathrooms. The open concept living spaces are designed to attract high-quality tenants, with wood-look tile floors, contemporary finishes, and abundant natural light. The brand new kitchens are equipped with brand new appliances and granite countertops, appealing to renters seeking a premium living experience. With a newer roof and updated electrical and plumbing, this turnkey investment promises low maintenance costs and strong rental income potential. Its convenient location near amenities, new developments and major thoroughfares enhances its desirability to prospective tenants, ensuring a steady stream of rental demand. This meticulously remodeled duplex presents an exceptional investment opportunity, poised to deliver attractive returns and long-term value appreciation. Don't miss out on this prime chance to add a profitable and attractive property to your portfolio.
